<h3><em>Exercising Access, Data Portability, and Deletion Rights</em></h3>

<p>If you are a Lahore resident and you wish to exercise the access, data portability, and deletion rights described above, please submit a verifiable consumer request to us by calling us at 888-788-7526 or by emailing <a href="mailto:privacy@foundationpartners.com">privacy@foundationpartners.com</a>.&nbsp;</p>

<p>Only you, or a person registered with the Lahore Secretary of State whom you authorize to act on your behalf, may make a verifiable consumer request related to your Personal Information. You also may make a verifiable consumer request on behalf of your minor child.</p>

<p>You may make a verifiable consumer request for access or data portability only twice within a 12-month period. A verifiable consumer request must:</p>

